024package org.opt4j.core;
025
026import java.util.Set;
027
028import com.google.inject.Inject;
029
030/**
031 * <p>
032 * The {@link Individual} class forms a single solution for the given
033 * optimization problem.
034 * </p>
035 * <p>
036 * An {@link Individual} contains the {@link Genotype}, phenotype {@link Object}
037 * , and {@link Objectives}: Initially, the {@link Individual} contains only a
038 * {@link Genotype}. The {@link org.opt4j.core.problem.Decoder} decodes the
039 * {@link Genotype} into a phenotype and adds it to the {@link Individual}.
040 * Finally, the phenotype is evaluated and the resulting {@link Objectives} are
041 * added to the {@link Individual}.
042 * </p>
043 * 
044 * @see Genotype
045 * @see Objectives
046 * @author glass, lukasiewycz
047 */
048public class Individual {
049
050        protected Genotype genotype;
051
052        protected Object phenotype;
053
054        protected Objectives objectives;
055
056        protected Set<IndividualStateListener> individualStateListeners;
057
058        protected State state = State.EMPTY;
059
060        /**
061         * The possible states of an {@link Individual}.
062         * 
063         * @author lukasiewycz
064         * 
065         */
066        public enum State {
067                /**
068                 * Initial state.
069                 */
070                EMPTY("empty", false, false, false),
071                /**
072                 * Individual has a {@link Genotype}.
073                 */
074                GENOTYPED("genotyped", false, false, false),
075                /**
076                 * Individual is currently being decoded.
077                 */
078                DECODING("decoding", false, false, true),
079                /**
080                 * Individual has a Phenotype, i.e. it is decoded.
081                 */
082                PHENOTYPED("phenotyped", true, false, false),
083                /**
084                 * Individual is currently being evaluated.
085                 */
086                EVALUATING("evaluating", true, false, true),
087                /**
088                 * Individual is evaluated.
089                 */
090                EVALUATED("evaluated", true, true, false);
091
092                private final String name;
093
094                private final boolean decoded;
095
096                private final boolean evaluated;
097
098                private final boolean processing;
099
100                /**
101                 * Defines a new State
102                 * 
103                 * @param name
104                 *            the full name of the state
105                 * @param decoded
106                 *            {@code true} if the individual is decoded in this state
107                 * @param evaluated
108                 *            {@code true} if the individual is evaluated in this state
109                 * @param processing
110                 *            {@code true} if the individual is processing in this state
111                 */
112                State(String name, boolean decoded, boolean evaluated, boolean processing) {
113                        this.name = name;
114                        this.decoded = decoded;
115                        this.evaluated = evaluated;
116                        this.processing = processing;
117                }
118
119                /**
120                 * Returns the specific name of the state.
121                 * 
122                 * @return the specific name of the state
123                 */
124                @Override
125                public String toString() {
126                        return name;
127                }
128
129                /**
130                 * Returns {@code true} if the individual is decoded in the current
131                 * state.
132                 * 
133                 * @return {@code true} if the individual is decoded in the current
134                 *         state
135                 */
136                public boolean isDecoded() {
137                        return decoded;
138                }
139
140                /**
141                 * Returns {@code true} if the individual is evaluated in the current
142                 * state.
143                 * 
144                 * @return {@code true} if the individual is evaluated in the current
145                 *         state
146                 */
147                public boolean isEvaluated() {
148                        return evaluated;
149                }
150
151                /**
152                 * Returns {@code true} if the individual is processing in the current
153                 * state.
154                 * 
155                 * @return {@code true} if the individual is processing in the current
156                 *         state
157                 */
158                public boolean isProcessing() {
159                        return processing;
160                }
161
162        }
163
164        /**
165         * Constructs an {@link Individual}.
166         */
167        @Inject
168        protected Individual() {
169                super();
170        }
171
172        /**
173         * Returns the phenotype.
174         * 
175         * @see #setPhenotype
176         * @return the phenotype
177         */
178        public Object getPhenotype() {
179                return phenotype;
180        }
181
182        /**
183         * Returns the objectives.
184         * 
185         * @see #setObjectives
186         * @return the objectives
187         */
188        public Objectives getObjectives() {
189                return objectives;
190        }
191
192        /**
193         * Returns the genotype.
194         * 
195         * @see #setGenotype
196         * @return the genotype
197         */
198        public Genotype getGenotype() {
199                return genotype;
200        }
201
202        /**
203         * Sets the genotype.
204         * 
205         * @see #getGenotype
206         * @param genotype
207         *            the genotype to be set
208         */
209        public void setGenotype(Genotype genotype) {
210                this.genotype = genotype;
211                setState(State.GENOTYPED);
212        }
213
214        /**
215         * Sets the phenotype.
216         * 
217         * @see #getPhenotype
218         * @param phenotype
219         *            the phenotype to be set
220         */
221        public void setPhenotype(Object phenotype) {
222                this.phenotype = phenotype;
223                setState(State.PHENOTYPED);
224        }
225
226        /**
227         * Sets the objectives.
228         * 
229         * @see #getObjectives
230         * @param objectives
231         *            the objectives to be set
232         */
233        public void setObjectives(Objectives objectives) {
234                this.objectives = objectives;
235                setState(State.EVALUATED);
236        }
237
238        /**
239         * Indicates whether this {@link Individual} is already decoded.
240         * 
241         * @return {@code true} if this individual is decoded
242         */
243        public boolean isDecoded() {
244                return state.isDecoded();
245        }
246
247        /**
248         * Indicates whether this {@link Individual} is already evaluated.
249         * 
250         * @return {@code true} if this inividual is evaluated
251         */
252        public boolean isEvaluated() {
253                return state.isEvaluated();
254        }
255
256        /**
257         * Sets the state of the {@link Individual}.
258         * 
259         * @see #getState
260         * @param state
261         *            the new status
262         */
263        public void setState(State state) {
264                if (this.state != state) {
265                        this.state = state;
266
267                        if (individualStateListeners != null) {
268                                for (IndividualStateListener listener : individualStateListeners) {
269                                        listener.inidividualStateChanged(this);
270                                }
271                        }
272                }
273        }
274
275        /**
276         * Returns the {@link State} of the {@link Individual}.
277         * 
278         * @see #setState
279         * @return the current state
280         */
281        public State getState() {
282                return state;
283        }
284
285        /**
286         * Sets the list of {@link IndividualStateListener}s that are called if the
287         * {@link State} of this individual changes.
288         * 
289         * @param individualStateListeners
290         *            the listener for a changing status.
291         */
292        protected void setIndividualStatusListeners(Set<IndividualStateListener> individualStateListeners) {
293                this.individualStateListeners = individualStateListeners;
294        }
295}
